videos.headline: Army's Hopkins scores 1st TD of season
videos.description: Kelvin Hopkins Jr. breaks through the Rice defense to score the two-yard touchdown to give Army a 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: Rice answers Army with 54-yd TD
videos.description: Nahshon Ellerbe ties the game at 7-7 as he jukes his way 54 yards for a Rice touchdown.
